02:58.136 --> 03:01.173
Yeah, there's a reason your mittens
need string, Epstein.

03:01.223 --> 03:03.760
That, and that everyone makes mistakes.

03:03.809 --> 03:05.640
But we are not everyone.

03:05.686 --> 03:08.598
We're coppers,
held at a higher standard.

03:08.647 --> 03:10.808
