That's what I thought.

03:49.980 --> 03:51.720
McNally, Interview One, now.

03:53.775 --> 03:55.766
Okay. I'll see you in a second.

04:01.616 --> 04:04.528
- Oh, hey! (laughs)
- (chuckles)

04:04.578 --> 04:05.738
(door closes)

04:07.247 --> 04:09.078
You left early this morning.

04:09.124 --> 04:12.082
Yeah, well, I had to drop some stuff off
at my dad's place.

04:12.127 --> 04:13.367
How is he?

04:13.420 --> 04:16.207
Good. He's the same.

04:16.256 --> 04:17.245
You know, why don't we, uh,

04:17.299 --> 04:18.709
why don't we take him out for dinner
this week?

04:18.759 --> 04:20.750
Sure.

04:20.802 --> 04:23.760
Yeah, let me just check and see,
uh, if he's free.

04:26.349 --> 04:29.841
Roster says that you're paired
with Swarek today.

04:29.895 --> 04:31.476
Since when do you check the roster?

04:31.521 --> 04:33.136
Eh, ljust want to know
who's got your back.

04:33.190 --> 04:34.270
(chuckles)

04:34.316 --> 04:35.931
Make sure you come home tonight.

04:36.485 --> 04:37.600
