35:45.310 --> 35:47.642
you might want to tell him
to lay off the heroics

35:47.687 --> 35:50.019
before he gets hurt
or sent back to jail.

35:52.192 --> 35:54.808
(Dov) Yes, sir, absolutely.

35:56.321 --> 35:58.186
Yeah? Looks like
he's got a hockey game.

35:58.239 --> 35:59.319
Get him out of here.

