37:09.644 --> 37:14.684
you just clean up your tunic
and put your crown back on.

37:21.573 --> 37:23.484
Dad?

37:23.533 --> 37:28.448
I thought maybe you should
look after this for a while.

37:29.664 --> 37:31.450
Sure.

37:31.499 --> 37:33.706
(siren wailing in distance)

37:33.752 --> 37:37.916
Dad, look, I really meant what I said.

37:45.597 --> 37:47.713
You know...

37:47.766 --> 37:51.634
the day they cut Kaliciak's deal,

37:51.686 --> 37:56.020
| asked if I could be the one
