37:56.065 --> 37:57.601
Tina's mother.

37:58.943 --> 38:02.435
| just wanted to say l was sorry.

38:04.616 --> 38:06.902
It was my fault. I screwed up.

38:06.951 --> 38:10.443
lwas drinking...
way too much.

38:13.291 --> 38:17.534
She made me a-a coffee
in the kitchen.

38:17.587 --> 38:20.875
l was standing
about 6 feet from her when...

38:20.924 --> 38:22.664
she put the knife to her chest.

38:24.719 --> 38:26.050
(sighs)

38:26.095 --> 38:27.380
The amount of force it takes

38:27.430 --> 38:31.218
to get a blade through the rib cage, l...

38:31.267 --> 38:32.768
I didn't think...

38:33.770 --> 38:35.761
There was so much blood.

38:37.440 --> 38:40.557
She slipped right through my arms,

38:41.903 --> 38:43.609
and she said,

38:43.655 --> 38:46.738
"| just want to be with my little girl."

38:54.624 --> 38:56.740
(voice breaks)
I didn't know.

38:58.962 --> 39:00.827
I can't lose you, Andy.

39:09.639 --> 39:11.846
I'll do whatever it takes.

