your superhero name?

39:55.727 --> 39:57.592
- What?
- Come on.

39:57.645 --> 39:59.510
Epstein, we all had 'em,
kids growing up.

39:59.564 --> 40:00.895
What was your superhero name?

40:01.941 --> 40:03.852
Oh.

40:03.902 --> 40:06.109
Well, mine was, um...

40:06.946 --> 40:07.935
"Justice Avenger."

40:07.989 --> 40:11.231
"Jus--" Nice. Nice.

40:11.284 --> 40:12.399
What about you?

40:12.452 --> 40:13.441
